	(28,NULL,2,'About us','about','<p><strong>Headway Institute FZ-LLC</strong> is an education centre offering a range of academic and non-academic courses in Dubai. Since its establishment in 2011, the institute has been providing customized training solutions in teaching English, Arabic, Russian, French, Italian, Spanish and other languages to academic institutions, corporate groups and individuals. It established a reputation for working creatively and adapting the courses to tight business schedules, specific subject areas and working environment of our clients.<br></p><p>The centre ensures high quality through employing the best possible talent in the market. Most of our teachers are qualified to a minimum Master’s level in language teaching or a related subject, have additional certificates in language teaching (CELTA, DELTA, TESOL, TOEFL) and have proven 5-15 years of experience in teaching to adult learners.\r\n</p><p>The training activities of the centre are properly licensed by the Dubai Technology and Media Free Zone Authority and Knowledge and Human Development Authority.\r\n</p>','About us | Headway Institute','About Headway Institute Headway Institute FZ-LLC is an education centre offering a range of academic and non-academic courses in Dubai.','','2015-08-27 08:37:30','2015-09-13 15:53:14',1,'',NULL),
	(29,NULL,2,'Courses','courses','<section class=\"languages\">\r\n<article class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<h3>Arabic Language Courses</h3>\r\n<img src=\"/images/ae.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language\" class=\"btn btn-default\">read more</a>\r\n</article>\r\n<article class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<h3>English Language Courses</h3>\r\n<img src=\"/images/en.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language\" class=\"btn btn-default\">read more</a>\r\n</article>\r\n<article class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<h3>Russian Language Courses</h3>\r\n<img src=\"/images/ru.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language\" class=\"btn btn-default\">read more</a></article></section>\r\n<h2>Corporate Language Training<br></h2>\r\n<p>Whatever your business needs, we offer language training programs that suite your companies specific requirement. We have a wide range of training methods and linguistic expertise to create well-planned programs that meet your companies needs flexibly and efficiently.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>We are also proud of our cutomized industry -pecific Russian language programs, such as Survival Russian (for company staff going to projects in Russain speaking countries) and Russian for Tourism and Hospitality, among many other.\r\n</p>\r\n<h2>Tutoring</h2>\r\n<p>ENGECON Dubai is offering private and group tutoring with qualified instructors. Our tutors are well-familiar with the school and university programs offered in Dubai, and experienced in helping the students achieve higher performance at school or university.\r\n</p>\r\n<h2>Business Training</h2>\r\n<p>We help our clients achieve maximum results from our customized learning solutions in such areas as Business and Intercultural Communications, Customer Service, Introduction to Internationa Financial Reporting, doing Business in Russia, to name a few.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Please call us at +971 4 3625313 / 17 / 19 or email to courses@headin.pro  for further information.\r\n</p>','Short Courses | Headway Insti