	(30,29,2,'Arabic Language Courses','arabic-language','<p><strong>Why learn Arabic in Dubai?</strong>\r\n</p><ul>\r\n	<li>Improve your career prospects in UAE</li>\r\n	<li>Make your travel in the region more rewarding and comfortable</li>\r\n	<li>Learn how to better understand your friends and colleagues</li>\r\n	<li>Understand the rich Arabic culture through its language</li>\r\n</ul><p>Headway Institute is there to help you by offering its expertise in teaching Arabic language and to make your Arabic learning experience an exciting journey.\r\n</p><h2>Learning Arabic with Headway Institute</h2><ul>\r\n	<li>Convenient location close to Dubai Marina, JLT, JBR and the Palm</li>\r\n	<li>Conversation-based method of teaching Arabic</li>\r\n	<li>Classes with experienced native-speaking Arabic teachers</li>\r\n	<li>Arabic lessons in small groups (4-8 people)</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible schedules ( morning, afternoon or evening), weekday and weekend classes</li>\r\n	<li>Affordable group rates, free trial lessons and frequent Arabic class promotions</li>\r\n	<li>Individual, semi-private and distance learning courses</li>\r\n</ul><h2>Our Courses</h2><ul>\r\n	<li><strong><a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/regular-arabic-courses\">Regular Arabic group courses</a></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Individual and small group lessons (2-3 people)</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/intensive-courses\">Intensive Arabic courses</a></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/corporate-courses\">Tailored corporate classes of Arabic</a></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>S</strong><strong>poken</strong><strong> /</strong> <strong>Conversational Arabic classes</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/arabic-for-children\">Arabic for children</a></strong><strong> and school tutoring</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Skype / online courses of Arabic</strong></li>\r\n</ul><h2>Arabic Class Schedule</h2><p>(click to view the schedule)\r\n</p><h2>Request more information       Register for  a course</h2>','Arabic Language Courses | Headway Institute','','','2015-08-27 08:43:41','2015-09-13 16:10:09',1,'<div class=\"list-group\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/intensive-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Intensive Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/arabic-for-children\" class=\"list-group-item\">Arabic for Children</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/corporate-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Corporate Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/regular-arabic-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Regular Arabic Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/private-arabic-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Private Arabic Courses</a>',NULL),
	(31,30,2,'Intensive Arabic Courses','intensive-courses','<p>Get enrolled to our intensive Arabic course in Dubai. The intensive course is preferable for those who are planning a holiday or a business trip, is going to get  a new job with demanding language requirements and is eager to acquire the knowledge of Arabic within the shortest time span.\r\n</p><p>The intensive course is focused on the four main language skills of speaking, listening, reading and writing with the main emphasis on interpersonal communication to help you develop fluency and confidence.\r\n</p><h2>Why choose the intesive course?</h2><ul>\r\n	<li>We use the communicative method of teaching which is based on language immersion, allows to learn the language in a short period of time and encourages alive communication</li>\r\n	<li>Teaching procedures involve the use of authentic Arabic learning materials which meet the global standards</li>\r\n	<li>All our  teachers are multilingual specialists experienced in dealing with groups of diversified language backgrounds</li>\r\n	<li>You use your in-class time with optimum efficiency</li>\r\n	<li>We offer a rich variety of study modes</li>\r\n</ul><h2>Modes of study</h2><p><strong>Individual  </strong>format integrates dynamic, one-to-one tuition and a syllabus drafted  to conform to your personal needs.\r\n</p><p><strong>Minigroup </strong>format allows obtaining the personal attention, as well as practicing Arabic with other participants.\r\n</p><p><strong>Group </strong>format offers the cost-effective opportunity to put the acquired knowledge into practice  through a range of communicative tasks, such as discussions, debates, role-play and pair-work.\r\n</p><h2>Arabic Intensive Course Levels</h2><table class=\"table table-striped table-bordered\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Beginner\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Elementary\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Pre-Intermediate\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Intermediate\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Upper-Intermediate\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Advanced\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table><p>Every level comprises 48 academic hours (an academic hour equals 45 minutes) – 24 lessons with the duration of  an hour and a half each. A course lasts 2  weeks. To find out your level, please send an inquiry for a placement test and send it to <a href=\"mailto:courses@headin.pro\">courses@headin.pro</a> upon completion.\r\n</p><h2>Accomodation rates and visa support </h2><ul>\r\n	<li>A double room in a 3-star hotel within walking distance from the institute starts from 525$ for 14 nights, breakfast included</li>\r\n	<li>The visa fee (up to 30 days’ stay) is 80$.</li>\r\n</ul><h2>Intensive Arabic Course Fees</h2><p><em>Please <strong>register for an Intensive Arabic course</strong> online or call our Certificate Programs Coordinator at +971 4 3625313/17/19, e-mail: </em><em><a href=\"mailto:courses@rudubai.ru\">courses@h</a><a href=\"mailto:courses@headin.pro\">eadin.pro</a>.</em>\r\n</p><table class=\"table table-striped table-bordered\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Form of study\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Price for 1 level (48 academic hours)\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Private\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>7,200 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Semi-private (2-3 people)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>5,280 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Group (4-8 people))\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>2,640 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','Intensive Arabic Courses | Headway Institute','','','2015-08-27 08:46