	(32,30,2,'Arabic for Children','arabic-for-children','<p><strong>Arabic for Children </strong>is is a group or a personalized Arabic course at a flexible schedule that includes classes from beginners’ to intermediate levels. The program is covering the essentials of Arabic language in a playful manner suitable for kids. Our dedicated tutors and teachers offer school catch up sessions and Arabic school exam preparation to kids of all ages.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>In Personalized Arabic Tutoring sessions we develop a customized Arabic study plan for kids and the Arabic lessons are based on each child\'s learning style and pace. We teach kids practical Arabic skills that are most useful in everyday and school life.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>In these Arabic classes, kids will receive systematic training in four aspects: listening, speaking, reading and writing. A variety of interesting topics will make your child learn Arabic with fun and high efficiency.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><br>Classes with both native and educated foreign speakers of Arabic are available.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Group sessions are subject to availability.\r\n</p>\r\n<h2>Convinient Location</h2>\r\n<p>Our institute offers a Arabic courses for kids with experienced native speakers at Dubai Knowledge Village located close to such communities of new Dubai as Dubai Media City, Dubai Internet City, Dubai Marina, Palm Jumeirah, Jumeirah Lakes Towers (JLT), Jumeirah Beach Residence (JBR), Emirates Hills (The Greens, The Lakes and The Springs), and Tecom.\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>Regular Arabic for Children Course Fees</h3>\r\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-bordered\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Form of study\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Price for 1 academic hour (45 minutes)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Price for 1 level (24 academic hours)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Private\r