	(33,30,2,'Corporate Arabic Language Courses','corporate-courses','<p>Communication in the Arabic-speaking work environment would not seem challenging after a set of practical Arabic language classes with a professional instructor. Tailor-made to fit your work schedule, industry and country-specific, a corporate Arabic course can be conveniently held in your office in Dubai, Abu Dhabi or Sharjah.\r\n</p><h2>Our Experience</h2><ul>\r\n	<li>Proven methods and attention to quality,</li>\r\n	<li>Training solutions customized to the specific needs and objectives,</li>\r\n	<li>Experienced qualified and certified multi-lingual instructors,</li>\r\n	<li>Certificates of Achievement provided on request,</li>\r\n	<li>Trainings at flexible schedule in our clients’ premises,</li>\r\n	<li>Dedicated Corporate Relations Coordinator to monitor the quality and feedback,</li>\r\n	<li>Competitive Corporate Prices.</li>\r\n</ul><h2>Our Corporate Arabic Courses</h2><p>Our programs have been developed by a team of experienced language training professionals to meet you requirements in the following subject areas:\r\n</p><ul>\r\n	<li>Regular Arabic Courses (beginner to advanced),</li>\r\n	<li>Conversational Arabic (in Egyptian, Syrian, Lebanese or Gulf Arabic),</li>\r\n	<li>Arabic for Customer Service (adapted for hospitality, retail and other sectors),</li>\r\n	<li>Business Arabic,</li>\r\n	<li>Tailor –made courses as per your company training objectives.</li>\r\n</ul><p>We customize the content, the duration and the timings of our courses according to our clients’ learning objectives, schedule and participant background. Experienced, qualified and certified multi-lingual teachers and instructors will ensure smooth course delivery at our clients’ premises.  Proven methods and attention to detail produce tangible results.\r\n</p><p>A specially appointed <strong>Corporate Relations Coordinator</strong> makes sure our clients’ requirements are well communicated and feedback is accounted for 