	(34,29,2,'English Language Courses','english-language','<p>Globalization makes our planet a smaller place to live in, and at present the role of English is more significant than ever before as it serves a connecting link in international communication. If you are looking for a way to improve your your command of the language the English courses at Headway Institute (HI) in Dubai are coming to the rescue.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><strong>Curious Facts about English</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>English is the official language of the UK, the USA and other 56 countries</li>\r\n	<li>English is surprisingly  rich in synonyms</li>\r\n	<li>English grammar is considered to be one of the simplest and most logical grammatical  systems among Indo-European languages</li>\r\n	<li>In British English pronunciation says a lot about a speaker’s educational and social backgrounds.</li>\r\n	<li>Loan words generally preserve the original spelling</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Why learn English  with HI?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We use the communicative method of teaching which is based on language immersion, allows to learn the language in a short time span and encourages alive communication</li>\r\n	<li>Teaching procedures involve the use of  authenticBritish  learning materials which meet the global standards</li>\r\n	<li>Teaching process is geared to Russian native speakers</li>\r\n	<li>We offer a considerable variety of study modes such as individual, group, and minigroup classes</li>\r\n	<li>You can chooseissue-related courses(business course, English for tourism workers, preparation for TOEFL and IELTS). We can also tailor an individual-oriented  course according to your personal interests and goals</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Our English Language Programs</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Regular courses (Beginners’ to Advanced)</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://headin.pro/en/short-courses/english/intensive-english-courses\">Intensive courses</a></li>\r\n	<li>TOEFL and IELTS preparation</li>\r\n	<li>Business course</li>\r\n	<li>Private and semi-private personalized courses</li>\r\n	<li>Tailor-made corporate courses</li>\r\n	<li>English for tourism workers</li>\r\n	<li>Conversational English</li>\r\n	<li>English for lawyers</li>\r\n	<li>English for the oil and gas sector</li>\r\n	<li>English for kids</li>\r\n	<li>Online / Skype course</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Levels of the English Language</h2>\r\n<p>Every level comprises 2 stages, 24 academic hours each (an academic hour equals 45 minutes) – 12 lessons with the duration of  an hour and a half each. A course lasts about 4-6 weeks depending on the lesson frequency.\r\n</p>\r\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-bordered\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p><strong>Levels</strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p><strong>Courses</strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n		<p><strong>Beginners’ Level</strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Beginner-1\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Beginner-2\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n		<p><strong> Elementary  Level</strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Elementary-1\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Elementary-2\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n		<p><strong> Pre-Intermediate Level</strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Pre-Intermediate-1\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Pre-Intermediate-2\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n		<p><strong> Intermediate Level</strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Intermediate-1\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Intermediate-2\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n		<p><strong> Upper- Intermediate  Level</strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Upper-Intermediate-1\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Upper-Intermediate-2\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n		<p