	(35,34,2,'Intensive English Courses','intensive-courses','<p>Get enrolled to our intensive English course in Dubai. The intensive course is preferable for those who are planning a holiday or a business trip, is going to get a new job with demanding language requirements and is eager to acquire the knowledge of English within the shortest time span.\r\n</p><p>The intensive course is focused on the four main language skills of speaking, listening, reading and writing with the main emphasis on interpersonal communication to help you develop fluency and confidence.\r\n</p><h2>Why choose the intesive course?</h2><ul>\r\n	<li>We use the communicative method of teaching which is based on language immersion, allows to learn the language in a short period of time and encourages alive communication</li>\r\n	<li>Teaching procedures involve the use of authentic Arabic learning materials which meet the global standards</li>\r\n	<li>All our  teachers are multilingual specialists experienced in dealing with groups of diversified language backgrounds</li>\r\n	<li>You use your in-class time with optimum efficiency</li>\r\n	<li>We offer a rich variety of study modes</li>\r\n</ul><h2>Modes of study</h2><p><strong>Individual  </strong>format integrates dynamic, one-to-one tuition and a syllabus drafted  to conform to your personal needs.\r\n</p><p><strong>Minigroup </strong>format allows obtaining the personal attention, as well as practicing Arabic with other participants.\r\n</p><p><strong>Group </strong>format offers the cost-effective opportunity to put the acquired knowledge into practice  through a range of communicative tasks, such as discussions, debates, role-play and pair-work.\r\n</p><h2>English Intensive Course Levels</h2><table class=\"table table-striped table-bordered\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Beginner\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Elementary\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Pre-Intermediate\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Intermediate\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Upper-Intermediate\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Advanced\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table><p>Every level comprises 48 academic hours (an academic hour equals 45 minutes) – 24 lessons with the duration of  an hour and a half each. A course lasts 2  weeks. To find out your level, please send an inquiry for a placement test and send it to <a href=\"mailto:courses@headin.pro\">courses@headin.pro</a> upon completion.\r\n</p><h2>Accomodation rates and visa support </h2><ul>\r\n	<li>A double room in a 3-star hotel within walking distance from the institute starts from 525$ for 14 nights, breakfast included</li>\r\n	<li>The visa fee (up to 30 days’ stay) is 80$.</li>\r\n</ul><h2>Intensive Arabic Course Fees</h2><table class=\"table table-striped table-bordered\"><colgroup><col><col><col></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Form of study\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Price for 1 level (48 academic hours)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Private\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>7,200 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Semi-private (2-3 people)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>5,280 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Group (4-8 people)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>2,640 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table><p><em>Please <strong>register for an Intensive English course</strong> online or call our Certificate Programs Coordinator at +971 4 3625313/17/19, e-mail: </em><em><a href=\"mailto:courses@rudubai.ru\">courses@h</a><a href=\"mailto:courses@headin.pro\">eadin.pro</a>.</em>\r\n</p>','Intensive English Courses | Headway Institute','Intensive English Courses An intensive English weekend / summer program based on conversation (speaking and listening) with the essential minimum of reading and grammar is ideal for those looking to start speaking English quickly.','','2015-08-27 08:54:33','2015-09-13 19:18:35',1,'<div class=\"list-group\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/english-for-children\" class=\"list-group-item\">English for Children</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/corporate-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Corporate Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/toefl-ielts\" class=\"list-group-item\">TOEFL / IELTS</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/english-for-specific-purposes\" class=\"list-group-item\">English for Specific Purposes</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/regular-english-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Regular English Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/private-english-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Private English Courses</a>',NULL),
	(36,34,2,'English for Children','english-for-children','<p><strong>English for Kids</strong> is a perfect opportunity to learn or improve English for the children attending English schools. Taught as a second (ESL) or a foreign language, the program is covering the essentials of English schooling, elementary and more advanced levels, including the preparation for school entrance tests, IB and GSE.\r\n</p><p><strong>English Language Tutoring for Children </strong>is a personalized English course at a flexible schedule. Our dedicated English teachers offer all the necessary assistance in learning English, such as pre-schooling, school catch up sessions and English exam preparation to children of all ages.\r\n</p><p><strong>English Language Classes for Schools</strong> are an excellent opportunity to offer English language classes as a part of your school curriculum or as an extracurricular activity. English language course for the schoolchildren will be set at your school, and taught by experienced native-speaking English tutors qualified to Master’s and PhD level in linguistics and language teaching.\r\n</p><p><em>Please </em><strong><em>register for an English course</em></strong><em> online</em><em> or call our Certificate Programs Coordinator at +971 4 3625313/17/19, e-mail: <a href=\"mailto:courses@rudubai.ru\">courses@h</a><a href=\"mailto:courses@headin.pro\">eadin.pro</a></em>.\r\n</p>','English for Children | Headway Institute','','','2015-08-27 08:56:31','2015-09-13 19:20:22',1,'<div class=\"list-group\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/intensive-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Intensive Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/corporate-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Corporate Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/toefl-ielts\" class=\"list-group-item\">TOEFL / IELTS</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/english-for-specific-purposes\" class=\"list-group-item\">English for Specific Purposes</a>\r\n<a 