	(37,34,2,'Corporate English Language Courses','corporate-courses','<p>Communication in the English-speaking environment of Dubai would not seem such a challenge after a set of practical English language classes with a professional instructor. Tailor-made to fit your work schedule and industry-specific, a corporate English course can be conveniently held in your office in Dubai, Abu Dhabi or Sharjah.\r\n</p><h2>International Oriental Academy Experience</h2><ul>\r\n	<li>Proven methods and attention to quality,</li>\r\n	<li>Training solutions customized to the specific needs and objectives,</li>\r\n	<li>Experienced qualified and certified multi-lingual instructors,</li>\r\n	<li>Certificates of Achievement provided on request,</li>\r\n	<li>Trainings at flexible schedule in our clients’ premises,</li>\r\n	<li>Dedicated Corporate Relations Coordinator to monitor the quality and feedback,</li>\r\n	<li>Competitive Corporate Prices</li>\r\n</ul><h2>Our Corporate English Courses</h2><p>Our programs have been developed by a team of experienced language training professionals to meet you requirements in the following subject areas:\r\n</p><ul>\r\n	<li>Regular English Courses,</li>\r\n	<li>English for Customer Service (adapted for hospitality, retail and other sectors),</li>\r\n	<li>English for Specific Purposes (sales, real estate, hospitality, oil and gas),</li>\r\n	<li>Business English,</li>\r\n	<li>English Language for Russian speakers (adapted to the level and purpose),</li>\r\n	<li>English Language for Arabic speakers (adapted to the level and purpose),</li>\r\n	<li>Tailor –made courses as per your company learning objectives.</li>\r\n</ul><p>We customize the content, the duration and the timings of our courses according to our clients’ learning objectives, schedule and participant background. Experienced, qualified and certified multi-lingual teachers and instructors will ensure smooth course delivery at our clients’ premises.  Proven methods and attention to detail produce tangible results.\r\n</p><p>A specially appointed <strong>Corporate Relations Coordinator</strong> makes sure our clients’ requirements are well communicated and feedback is accounted for in the process of course delivery.\r\n</p><h2>Competitive Corporate Rates</h2><p>Since all our corporate courses are tailor-made we are adjusting our pricing to meet our clients’ budget requirements too. Please, send an e-mail to <a href=\"mailto:courses@rudubai.ru\">courses@h</a><a href=\"mailto:courses@headin.pro\">eadin.pro</a> to get your personalized quote.\r\n</p>','Corporate English Language Courses | Headway Institute','','','2015-08-27 08:57:50','2015-09-13 19:21:51',1,'<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/intensive-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Intensive Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/english-for-children\" class=\"list-group-item\">English for Children</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/toefl-ielts\" class=\"list-group-item\">TOEFL / IELTS</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/english-for-specific-purposes\" class=\"list-group-item\">English for Specific Purposes</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/regular-english-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Regular English Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/private-english-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Private English Courses</a>',NULL),
	(38,34,2,'TOEFL / IELTS Preparation Courses','toefl-ielts','<p><strong>TOEFL (Test of English as a Foreign Language)</strong> and IELTS (<strong>International English Language Testing System) are</strong> the most well-known internationally accredited tests of proficiency in English and are accepted world-wide as a proof of one’s skills in the English language. Our test prep course helps students familiarize themselves with the general reading, listening, speaking and writing skills measured on the test, as well as address their personal learning difficulties.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Our personalized <strong>TOEFL iBT and PBT Exam Preparation</strong> courses will help you achieve a high score on your TOEFL exam by teaching you how to apply the test-taking strategies and improving the academic English skills needed for success at the exam. The course syllabus includes the TOEFL-focused listening, speaking reading and writing, plus sample questions and practice tests.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Our <strong>IELTS Preparation</strong> course will increase your chance of getting the desired score by providing you with the best personalized advice on test-taking strategies and expert assistance in the development of the language and academic skills needed to pass the test successfully.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>By taking out test preparation courses you will:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>get an internationally qualified teacher with test-taking experience,</li>\r\n	<li>get to know about the test format and question types using the latest exam preparation materials,</li>\r\n	<li>improve your reading, writing,  listening and speaking skills,</li>\r\n	<li>learn effective test and time-management strategies,</li>\r\n	<li>practise sample test tasks and sample exams in simulated test environment.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Test Preparation Course Fees</h2>\r\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-bordered\"><colgroup><col><col><col></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Form of study\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Price for 1 academic hour (45 minutes)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Price for 1 level (48 academic hours)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Private\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>150 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>7,200 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Semi-private (2-3 people)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>110 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>5,280 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Group (4-8 people)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>55 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>2,640 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><em>Please <strong>register for an English course</strong> online or call our Certificate Programs Coordinator at +971 4 3625313/17/19, e-mail: </em><em><a href=\"mailto:courses@headin.pro\">courses@headin.pro</a>.</em>\r\n</p>','TOEFL / IELTS Preparation Courses | Headway Institute','','','2015-08-27 08:59:23','2015-09-13 19:28:24',1,'<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/intensive-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Intensive Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/english-for-children\" class=\"list-group-item\">English for Children</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/corporate-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Corporate Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/english-for-specific-purposes\" class=\"list-group-item\">English for Specific Purposes</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/regular-english-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Regular English Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/private-english-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Private English Courses</a>',NULL),
	(39,34,2,'English for Specific Purposes','english-for-specific-purposes','<p>These specific English courses are designed for student willing to improve their English language skills for work or study in a particular field, such as Tourism and Hospitality, Retail, Trading, academia and others. The classes can be taken as a part of a corporate, private or distant learning course of English.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>We deliver the following ESP courses:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Business English,</li>\r\n	<li>English communication skills,</li>\r\n	<li>Legal English,</li>\r\n	<li>Academic English and writing,</li>\r\n	<li>English for Customer Service (adapted for hospitality, retail and other sectors),</li>\r\n	<li>English for Hospitality (for English and Russian speakers),</li>\r\n	<li>English for Retail,</li>\r\n	<li>English for Oil and Gas Industry.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Business English and Communication</h2>\r\n<p>This course provides business English training to international company employees, managers and executives who compete in today’s global market.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Developed according to the latest business practices this course is aimed at written and verbal skills necessary for successful performance in a variety of business contexts, i.e. presentations, meetings, and negotiations. It also includes supporting vocabulary, grammar, pronunciation and cultural information.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Our Business and Communication Courses typically include the following sections:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Powerful Presentations - the essentials of presenting in English,</li>\r\n	<li>Meeting & Discussions - we discuss key communication strategies used in meetings: presenting a plan, pitching alternatives, expressing opinions, disagreeing, and forming questions,</li>\r\n	<li>Winning Negotiations - teaches what to say in all phases of negotiating,</li>\r\n	<li>Effective Business Writing - the essentials, such as conciseness, clarity, the correct tone and the importance of using action verbs. We review sentence length, using bullets, and vocabulary: general & business, written & spoken, direct & indirect,</li>\r\n	<li>Telephone conversation techniques – the essentials of listening and speaking over the telephone, including the telephone etiquette,</li>\r\n	<li>Optional industry-specific or functional modules (marketing, finance, hospitality, tourism, oil and gas, legal and more),</li>\r\n	<li>Communicating Across Cultures - we discuss the business etiquette and communication styles and norms of different countries and cultures - not just the words, but also the message behind the words,</li>\r\n	<li>English Language Review - we review the range of English verb tenses, prepositions, modals - (could, would, should), articles, and vocabulary expansion,</li>\r\n	<li>Business vocabulary  (general managerial  and business terms, organizational structure).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Legal English</h2>\r\n<p>This course is aimed at for people working in international law field and students planning their careers in the legal field. It develops the real-life English language skills necessary for communication in international legal context, such as understanding and usage of specialized legal terms, legal document comprehension and writing, necessary grammar, style and more.<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>We use original legal documents and law school textbooks, such as “Gilbert Law Summaries” and “Emanuel Law Outlines” are used in the course.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Our Business and Communication Courses typically include the following sections:\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Contracts Law</li>\r\n	<li>Corporate Law</li>\r\n	<li>Law of Property</li>\r\n	<li>Bankruptcy</li>\r\n	<li>Commercial Paper</li>\r\n	<li>Wills and Trusts</li>\r\n	<li>Securities Regulation</li>\r\n	<li>Family Law</li>\r\n	<li>Criminal Law</li>\r\n	<li>Torts</li>\r\n	<li>Taxation</li>\r\n	<li>Banking</li>\r\n	<li>Conflict of Laws</li>\r\n	<li>Administrative Law</li>\r\n	<li>Legal Research and Writing</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>English for Academic Purposes</h2>\r\n<p>This course focuses on skills and strategies required to perform in English-speaking university setting, such as grammar, vocabulary and forms of expression, text comprehension and critical analysis, essay writing. The program may also be adjusted to provide more narrow focus on the more specific linguistic demands of a particular area of study, for example business subjects, social science, legal studies.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>The course would typically include:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Critical reading techniques</li>\r\n	<li>Active listening skills</li>\r\n	<li>Academic writing (essays, reports, dissertation)</li>\r\n	<li>Presentation skills</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>English for Customer Service (Hospitality, Retail, Real estate)</h2>\r\n<p>This programme can be tailor-made to suit both those stating their career in the industry and mid-career and executive managers willing to expand their skills internationally.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Developed by a team of linguists and customer service consultants, conversational courses for the front desk customer service staff are focused around the essential communication skills and everyday situations they could encounter at work.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Management-level courses also include Business English and written communication modules, such as negotiation and telephone techniques, writing e-mails, business etiquette specific to the industry.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>The courses could be adapted to the native speakers of Russian and other languages.\r\n</p>\r\n<h2>English for Oil and Gas Industry</h2>\r\n<p>This course is an intermediate course for students studying for a career in the oil and gas industries, who will need English to communicate at work.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>The course could be adapted to include the topics and vocabulary from the oil and gas engineering, geophysical, business and other fields.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><em>For </em><strong><em>upcoming course dates </em></strong><em>please call our Certificate Programs Coordinator at +971 4 3625313/17/19, or e-mail to </em><a href=\"mailto:courses@headin.pro\"><em>courses@headin.pro</em></a><em>.</em>\r\n</p>','English for Specific Purposes | Headway Institute','','','2015-08-27 09:01:33','2015-09-13 19:29:34',1,'\r\n<div class=\"list-group\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/intensive-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Intensive Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/english-for-children\" class=\"list-group-item\">English for Children</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/corporate-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Corporate Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/toefl-ielts\" class=\"list-group-item\">TOEFL / IELTS</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/regular-english-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Regular English Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/private-english-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Private English Courses</a>',NULL),
	(40,29,2,'Russian Language Courses','russian-language','<p>Are you looking for an opportunity to sharpen your Russian language skills for either business or personal purposes? Or maybe you are planning to enter a Russian institution of higher education? Headway Institute is then, no doubt, the best option.\r\n</p><h2>Type of courses</h2><ul>\r\n	<li>Regular courses (Beginner to Advanced)</li>\r\n	<li>Conversational courses</li>\r\n	<li>Intensive courses</li>\r\n	<li>Test preparation courses (including TORFL)</li>\r\n	<li>Private and semi-private personalized courses</li>\r\n	<li>Tailor-made corporate courses</li>\r\n	<li>Online / Skype courses</li>\r\n	<li>Russian for specific purposes</li>\r\n	<li>Russian for children</li>\r\n</ul><p>Quick Facts about the Russian Language\r\n</p><ul>\r\n	<li>the largest native language in Europe, and the official language of Russia and 4 other countries</li>\r\n	<li>the seventh by total number of speakers in the World</li>\r\n	<li>one of the six official languages of the United Nations</li>\r\n	<li>one of the most useful languages to learn in terms of a gainful employment</li>\r\n	<li>less difficult to learn than its reputation claims</li>\r\n</ul><h2>We suggests:</h2><ol>\r\n	<li>Classical approach to the Russian language studies which is based on grammar rules  exploration with further  communication skills development to achieve maximum effectiveness of student’s performance</li>\r\n	<li>Authentic Russian learning materials containing a variety of true-to-life situations to familiarize the students with the language in a constantly changing universe</li>\r\n	<li>Professional tutors from Russia and CIS countries qualified to Master’s and PhD level in Russian as a foreign languageteaching</li>\r\n	<li>A wide range of study modes such as individual, group, and minigroup classes</li>\r\n	<li>Morning, afternoon, evening and weekend Russian classes (depending on availability)</li>\r\n	<li>Issue-related courses to your choice (business course, Russian for tourism, courses for university enrollees, specially designed courses)</li>\r\n	<li>Language immersion through communication with native speakers, watching movies, as well as reading Russian literature and national press</li>\r\n</ol><h2>Russian Language Programs</h2><p>Headway Institute provides  a bunch  of Russian courses with skillful native speakers at Dubai Knowledge Village, located close to such communities of new Dubai as Dubai Media City, Dubai Internet City, Dubai Marina, Palm Jumeirah, Jumeirah Lakes Towers (JLT), Jumeirah Beach Residence (JBR), Emirates Hills (The Greens, The Lakes and The Springs) and Tecom.\r\n</p><p>Our Russian studies are performed in both English and Arabic as the languages of instruction.\r\n</p><h2>Russian Language Levels</h2><p>Every level embraces 2 sublevels, 24 academic hours each (an academic hour equals 45 minutes).\r\n</p><p>A course should take around 4-6 week to accomplish with a group.\r\n</p><table class=\"table table-striped table-bordered\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Levels\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Courses\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n		<p>Beginners’ Level\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Beginner-1\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Beginner-2\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n		<p>Elementary  Level\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Elementary-1\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Elementary-2\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n		<p>Pre-Intermediate Level\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Pre-Intermediate-1\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Pre-Intermediate-2\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n		<p> Intermediate Level\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Intermediate-1\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Intermedi