	(41,40,2,'Intensive Russian Courses','intensive-courses','<p>An intensive Russian program based on conversation (speaking and listening) with the essential minimum of reading and grammar is ideal for those looking to start speaking Russian quickly. It is perfect for those going to Russia soon for business or leisure.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><strong>Private tuition</strong> combines highly concentrated, one-to-one instruction and a curriculum targeted specially to your individual needs. <strong>Semi-private (small group)</strong> <strong>classes </strong>allow getting the personal attention you need, as well practicing Russian with other group members. <strong>Group courses</strong> offer the cost-effective alternative and an opportunity to master spoken Russian language through discussions, debates and conversation activities, such as role-play and pair-work.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>All classes are led by qualified native Russian teachers experienced in helping learners of different nationalities enhance their Russian language skills.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>By taking out Intensive Russian courses you will:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>get an internationally qualified teacher with ample experience in teaching Russian to adults,</li>\r\n	<li>improve your reading, writing,  listening and speaking skills using the latest Russian language learning packs and materials,</li>\r\n	<li>use your class learning time with maximum efficiency,</li>\r\n	<li>practise conversation in intensive format with your group members and your instructor.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Intensive Russian Course Fees</h2>\r\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-bordered\"><colgroup><col><col><col></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Form of study\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Price for 1 academic hour (45 minutes)\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Price for 1 level (48 academic hours)\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>Private\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>150 AED\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>7,200 AED\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>Semi-private (2-3 people)\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>110 AED\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>5,280 AED\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>Group (4-8 people)\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>55 AED\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>2,640 AED\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><em>Please <strong>register for an Intensive Russian course</strong> online or call our Certificate Programs Coordinator at +971 4 3625313/17/19, e-mail: <a href=\"mailto:courses@headin.pro\">courses@headin.pro</a>.</em>\r\n</p>','Intensive Russian Courses | Headway Institute','','','2015-08-27 09:06:32','2015-09-13 19:56:07',1,'<div class=\"list-group\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/russian-language-for-children\" class=\"list-group-item\">Russian Language for Children</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/russian-test-preparation\" class=\"list-group-item\">Russian Test Preparation</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/regular-russian-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Regular Russian Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/corporate-russian-language-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Corporate Russian Language</a>',NULL),
	(42,40,2,'Russian language for children','russian-language-for-children','<p>Russian for Kids is a perfect choice for native or bilingual Russian speaking children going to international schools. The program is covering the essentials of Russian kindergarten schooling and includes Russian Language and Literature, Drawing, Arts and Crafts. Elementary and secondary school children can cover the basics of Russian school program with Russian Language and Literature classes, celebrate Russian holidays and get other insights into Russian culture. Russian for Kids course is run in specialized groups depending on the Russian skills level and age.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Russian Language Tutoring for Children is a personalized Russian course at a flexible schedule. Our dedicated Russian teachers offer all the necessary assistance in learning Russian, such as pre-schooling, school catch up sessions and Russian GSE/IB exam preparation to children of all ages.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Russian Language Lessons for Schools are an excellent opportunity to offer Russian language classes as a second language or the foreign language in school curriculum, or as an extracurricular activity. Russian language course for the schoolchildren will be set at your school, and taught by experienced native-speaking Russian tutors qualified to Master’s and PhD level in linguistics and language teaching.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>We are running Russian language classes in several international schools of Dubai. Please contact us if you would like us to arrange Russian language courses in your school.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>The children will learn how to speak, read and think in Russian properly at our classes.  Folk stories, fairytales, books by Russian writers and poets will give them wonderful moments. Writing essays and dictations which will help them to develop good grammar skills and improve the vocabulary.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Advantages of studying Russian Language at Headway Institute:\r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Our curriculum is based on 