	(43,40,2,'Russian Test Preparation','russian-test-preparation','<p><strong>TORFL (Testing of Russian as a Foreign Language)</strong> is an internationally accredited test of proficiency in Russian. It is established as a part of the Association of Language Testers in Europe (ALTE) and is accepted world-wide as a proof of one’s skills in the Russian language.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><strong>Elementary TORFL Preparation Course</strong> is aimed at upgrading language skills of those who completed a regular Russian Elementary-2 course to a TORFL Certificate level (A-1). Starting every summer.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><strong>Basic TORFL Preparation Course</strong> is an intensive course aimed at upgrading the language skills of those who completed a regular Russian Intermediate-2 course to a TORFL Certificate level. Starting every autumn.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><strong>Russian for Academic Purposes (TORFL-1 Preparation Course</strong>) is a super-intensive course aimed at upgrading the language skills of those who completed a regular RussianAdvanced-2 course to a TORFL Certificate, Level 1. Starting every winter.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><strong>Russian University Entrance Exam Preparation Courses </strong> are designed for both native Russian and bilingual speakers willing to be admitted to any other university in Russia.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><strong>Russian exam Preparation Courses for GSE/IB</strong> are tailor-made to deal with specific areas and skills that need improvement for the successful test passing.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><em>For <strong>upcoming course dates </strong>please call our Coordinator at +971 4 3625313/17/19, or e-mail to </em><a href=\"mailto:courses@headin.pro\"><em>courses@headin.pro</em></a><em>.</em>\r\n</p>','Russian Test Preparation Courses | Headway Institute','','','2015-08-27 09:11:13','2015-09-13 20:19:08',1,'<div class=\"list-group\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/intensive-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Intensive Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/russia