	(55,NULL,1,'Главная','/','<section class=\"languages\">\r\n<article class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<h3>Курсы арабского языка</h3>\r\n<img src=\"images/ae.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n<p>Бесспорно, одним из самых эффективных способов изучения языка, является обучение в стране, говорящей на этом языке. Курсы арабского языка Headway Institue (HI) в Дубае позволяют выучить арабский язык и закрепить навыки в повседневном общении с носителями языка.\r\n</p>\r\n<a href=\"/ru/courses/arabic-language\" class=\"btn btn-default\">подробнее</a>\r\n</article>\r\n<article class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<h3>Курсы английского языка</h3>\r\n<img src=\"images/en.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n<p>Если ваша цель- свободное владение английским языком, так необходимое для работы, образования, путешествий и повседневного общения в ОАЭ, достигнуть результата Вам помогут курсы английского языка Headway Institute (HI).\r\n</p>\r\n<a href=\"/ru/courses/english-language\" class=\"btn btn-default\">подробнее</a>\r\n</article>\r\n<article class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<h3>Курсы русского языка</h3>\r\n<img src=\"images/ru.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n<p>Если Вы хотите, чтобы супруг, друг или коллега заговорил на Вашем языке, ищете способ усовершенстовать Ваш русский для делового и личного общения, или решили поступить в российский ВУЗ, тогда курсы русского языка в Headway Institute представляют собой наилучшее решение.\r\n</p>\r\n<a href=\"/ru/courses/russian-language\" class=\"btn btn-default\">подробнее</a>\r\n</article>\r\n</section><section class=\"description\">\r\n</section>','Headway Institute','','','2015-08-31 08:40:08','2015-09-22 18:36:25',1,'','<img src=\"/images/students.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"no-img-responsive\">\r\n<div style=\"background-color: #f4f4f4;\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h3>Добро пожаловать в Headway Institute!</h3>\r\n<p>Название нашего института переводится с английского языка как «прогресс» и отражает наше стремление помочь нашим слушателям в достижении образовательных, карьерных и личных целей в разных областях знаний.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
	(56,NULL,2,'Home','/','<section class=\"content\"><section class=\"languages\">\r\n<article class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<h3>Arabic Language Courses</h3>\r\n<img src=\"images/ae.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Convenient location close to Dubai Marina, JLT, JBR and the Palm</li>\r\n	<li>Conversation-based method of teaching Arabic</li>\r\n	<li>Classes with experienced native-speaking Arabic teachers</li>\r\n	<li>Arabic lessons in small groups (4-8 people)</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible schedules ( morning, afternoon or evening), weekday and weekend classes</li>\r\n	<li>Affordable group rates, free trial lessons and frequent Arabic class promotions</li>\r\n	<li>Individual, semi-private and distance learning courses</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language\" class=\"btn btn-default\">read more</a>\r\n</article>\r\n<article class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<h3>English Language Courses</h3>\r\n<img src=\"images/en.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We use the communicative method of teaching which is based on language immersion, allows to learn the language in a short time span and encourages alive communication</li>\r\n	<li>Teaching procedures involve the use of  authenticBritish  learning materials which meet the global standards</li>\r\n	<li>Teaching process is geared to Russian native speakers</li>\r\n	<li>We offer a considerable variety of study modes such as individual, group, and minigroup classes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language\" class=\"btn btn-default\">read more</a>\r\n</article>\r\n<article class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<h3>Russian Language Courses</h3>\r\n<img src=\"images/ru.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Classical approach to the Russian language studies which is based on grammar rules  exploration with further  communication skills development to achieve maximum effectiveness of student’s performance</li>\r\n	<li>Authentic Russian learning materials containing a variety of true-to-life situations to familiarize the students with the language in a constantly changing universe</li>\r\n	<li>Professional tutors from Russia and CIS countries qualified to Master’s and PhD level in Russian as a foreign languageteaching</li>\r\n	<li>A wide range of study modes such as individual, group, and minigroup classes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language\" class=\"btn btn-default\">read more</a></article></section>\r\n<section class=\"description\">\r\n</section>\r\n</section>','Headway Institute','','','2015-08-31 09:04:19','2015-09-22 18:33:19',1,'','<img src=\"/images/students.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"no-img-responsive\">\r\n<div style=\"background-color: #f4f4f4;\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h3>Welcome to Headway Institute!</h3>\r\n<p>As our name suggests, we are dedicated to helping our students reach their academic, career and personal goals by improving their skills in a variety of fields.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
	(57,30,2,'Regular Arabic Courses','regular-arabic-courses','<p>Our Arabic certificate programme consists of eight levels and is focused on Arabic conversation, basic reading (including the alphabet) and essential grammar. Based on Standard Arabic language, the curriculum includes conversational practice in Lebanese, Syrian, Gulf, Egyptian and other Arabic dialects.\r\n</p><p>Our programme is structured as per the internationally recognized Common European Framework of Reference for Languages (CEFR) and includes the following courses:\r\n</p><ul>\r\n	<li>Beginner Arabic Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Beginner Arabic Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Elementary Arabic Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Elementary Arabic Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Pre-Intermediate Arabic Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Pre-Intermediate Arabic Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Intermediate Arabic Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Intermediate Arabic Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Upper-Intermediate Arabic Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Upper-Intermediate Arabic Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced Arabic Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced Arabic Course 2</li>\r\n</ul><h2>Group Courses</h2><p>Every group course fits within above-mentioned framework and lasts from 4 to 6 weeks, depending on the class frequency.\r\n</p><p>Advantages of learning Arabic in a group:\r\n</p><ul>\r\n	<li>More entertaining and dynamic classes</li>\r\n	<li>Better motivation and commitment</li>\r\n	<li>Leaning form classmates</li>\r\n	<li>More conversational practice</li>\r\n</ul><h2>Individual Classes</h2><p>Private and semi-private classes are tailored as per the student requirements and run at flexible timings.\r\n</p><p>Advantages of learning Arabic in a private mode:\r\n</p><ul>\r\n	<li>The course content is adjusted to specific learning goals and needs</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible schedule</li>\r\n	<li>Ideal for people who travel frequently</li>\r\n	<li>An opportunity to learn Arabic with friends, family or colleagues</li>\r\n</ul><h2>Course Fees</h2><p>Each course comprises 24 academic hours (45 minutes).\r\n</p><table class=\"table table-striped table-bordered\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Group (4-8 people)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>1 320 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Semi-private (2-3 people)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>2 640 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Private\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>3 600 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table><h2><br></h2>','Regular Arabic Courses','','','2015-08-31 17:12:24','2015-09-13 17:07:28',1,'<div class=\"list-group\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/intensive-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Intensive Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/arabic-for-children\" class=\"list-group-item\">Arabic for Children</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/corporate-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Corporate Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/private-arabic-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Private Arabic Courses</a>',NULL),
	(58,30,2,'Private Arabic Courses','private-arabic-courses','<p>These tailored courses provide focus on specific learning goal, a particular dialect of Arabic, a special subject area or industry. They are usually run on individual basis (private, semi-private, corporate or private group, on distance-learning basis), and are unique for each client and student. Flexible schedule, start date and personalized approach are among the benefits of these courses.\r\n</p><p>The focus areas of learning Arabic in an individual programme include, but are not limited to:\r\n</p><ul>\r\n	<li>Grammar, speaking, writing or reading</li>\r\n	<li>Arabic examination/test preparation</li>\r\n	<li>Arabic for customer service, hospitality, retail</li>\r\n	<li>Arabic language and culture</li>\r\n	<li>Business Arabic</li>\r\n</ul><p>We provide tailored training in the following dialects of Arabic language:\r\n</p><ul>\r\n	<li>Classical Arabic (the language of Quran)</li>\r\n	<li>Fusha / Standard Arabic</li>\r\n	<li>Gulf Arabic</li>\r\n	<li>Lebanese / Syrian / Jordanian Arabic</li>\r\n	<li>Egyptian Arabic</li>\r\n</ul><h2>Course Fees</h2><p>Each course comprises 24 academic hours (45 minutes).\r\n</p><table class=\"table table-striped table-bordered\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Group (4-8 people)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>1 320 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Semi-private (2-3 people)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>2 640 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>Private\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<p>3 600 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table><ul>\r\n	<li>Each course comprises 24 academic hours (45 minutes)</li>\r\n	<li>The prices are quoted per person</li>\r\n	<li>The given fees can vary depending on the content of the course</li>\r\n</ul><h2>Arabic Class Schedule</h2><p>You can start your private course any time subject to teacher’s availability.\r\n</p>','Private Arabic Courses','','','2015-08-31 17:18:30','2015-09-13 17:10:21',1,'<div class=\"list-group\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/intensive-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Intensive Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/arabic-for-children\" class=\"list-group-item\">Arabic for Children</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/corporate-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Corporate Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/arabic-language/regular-arabic-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Regular Arabic Courses</a>',NULL),
	(59,34,2,'Regular English Courses','regular-english-courses','<p>Our regular English programme is comprised of eight levels and is aimed at the development of the essential skills, necessary for successful communication in English language. The latest communicative methods and a well-balanced combination of such activities as reading, speaking, listening and writing makes this programme the right one regardless of the learning goals.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Our programme is structured as per the internationally recognized Common European Framework of Reference for Languages (CEFR) and includes the following courses:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Beginner English Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Beginner English Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Elementary English Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Elementary English Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Pre-Intermediate English Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Pre-Intermediate English Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Intermediate English Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Intermediate English Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Upper-Intermediate English Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Upper-Intermediate English Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced English Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced English Course 2</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Group Courses</h2>\r\n<p>Every group course fits within above-mentioned framework and lasts from 4 to 6 weeks, depending on the class frequency.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Advantages of learning English in a group:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>More entertaining and dynamic classes</li>\r\n	<li>Better motivation and commitment</li>\r\n	<li>Leaning form classmates</li>\r\n	<li>More conversational practice</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Individual Classes</h2>\r\n<p>Private and semi-private classes are tailored as per the student requirements and run at flexible timings.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Advantages of learning English in a private mode:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The course content is adjusted to specific learning goals and needs</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible schedule</li>\r\n	<li>Ideal for people who travel frequently</li>\r\n	<li>An opportunity to learn English with f