	(60,34,2,'Private English Courses','private-english-courses','<p>These tailored courses provide focus on a specific learning goals, a particular subject area or industry. They are usually run on individual basis (private, semi-private, corporate or private group, on distance-learning basis), and are unique for each client and student. Flexible schedule and personalized approach are among the benefits of these courses. They are also a perfect choice for examination preparation, since they allow addressing individual problem areas.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>The focus areas of learning English in an individual programme include, but are not limited to:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Grammar, speaking, writing or reading</li>\r\n	<li>English examination/test preparation (IELTS, TOEFL, and others)</li>\r\n	<li>English for customer service, hospitality, retail</li>\r\n	<li>English for oil and gas industry</li>\r\n	<li>Legal English</li>\r\n	<li>Business English and business communications in English</li>\r\n	<li>English for Russian speakers</li>\r\n	<li>English for schoolchildren (British, American and international curriculum)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Course Fees</h2>\r\n<p>Each course comprises 24 academic hours (45 minutes).\r\n</p>\r\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-bordered\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Group (4-8 people)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>1 320 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Semi-private (2-3 people)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>2 640 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Private\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>3 600 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Each course comprises 24 academic hours (45 minutes)</li>\r\n	<li>The prices are quoted per person</li>\r\n	<li>The given fees can vary depending on the content of the course</li>\r\n</ul>','Private English Courses','','','2015-08-31 17:21:33','2015-09-13 19:52:15',1,'<div class=\"list-group\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/intensive-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Intensive Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/english-for-children\" class=\"list-group-item\">English for Children</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/corporate-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Corporate Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/toefl-ielts\" class=\"list-group-item\">TOEFL / IELTS</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/english-for-specific-purposes\" class=\"list-group-item\">English for Specific Purposes</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/english-language/regular-english-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Regular English Courses</a>',NULL),
	(61,40,2,'Regular Russian Courses','regular-russian-courses','<p>Our Russian language programme consists of eight levels and targets the development of verbal and written communication skills with the focus on conversation. The latest communicative methods make it possible to start speaking and reading Russian at the levels, necessary for successful communication with native Russian speakers.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Our programme is structured as per the internationally recognized Common European Framework of Reference for Languages (CEFR) and includes the following courses:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Beginner Russian Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Beginner Russian Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Elementary Russian Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Elementary Russian Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Pre-Intermediate Russian Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Pre-Intermediate Russian Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Intermediate Russian Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Intermediate Russian Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Upper-Intermediate Russian Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Upper-Intermediate Russian Course 2</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced Russian Course 1</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced Russian Course 2</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Group Courses</h2>\r\n<p>Every group course fits within above-mentioned framework and lasts from 4 to 6 weeks, depending on the class frequency.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Advantages of learning Russian in a group:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>More entertaining and dynamic classes</li>\r\n	<li>Better motivation and commitment</li>\r\n	<li>Leaning form classmates</li>\r\n	<li>More conversational practice</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Individual Classes</h2>\r\n<p>Private and semi-private classes are tailored as per the student requirements and run at flexible timings.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Advantages of learning Russian in a private mode:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The course content is adjusted to specific learning goals and needs</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible schedule</li>\r\n	<li>Ideal for people who travel frequently</li>\r\n	<li>An opportunity to learn Russian with friends, family or colleagues</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Course Fees</h2>\r\n<p>Each course comprises 24 academic hours (45 minutes).\r\n</p>\r\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-bordered\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Group (4-8 people)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>1 320 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Semi-private (2-3 people)\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>2 640 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>Private\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<p>3 600 AED\r\n		</p>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','Regular Russian Courses','','','2015-08-31 17:24:09','2015-09-13 20:21:11',1,'<div class=\"list-group\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/intensive-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Intensive Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/russian-language-for-children\" class=\"list-group-item\">Russian Language for Children</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/russian-test-preparation\" class=\"list-group-item\">Russian Test Preparation</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/corporate-russian-language-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Corporate Russian Language</a>',NULL),
	(62,40,2,'Corporate Russian Language','corporate-russian-language-courses','<p>Communication in the Russian-speaking country would not seem challenging after a set of practical Russian language classes with a professional instructor. Tailor-made to fit your work schedule and industry-specific, a corporate Russian course can be conveniently held in your office in Dubai, Abu Dhabi or Sharjah.\r\n</p>\r\n<h2>Our Experience</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Proven methods and attention to quality,</li>\r\n	<li>Training solutions customized to the specific needs and objectives,</li>\r\n	<li>Experienced qualified and certified multi-lingual instructors,</li>\r\n	<li>Certificates of Achievement provided on request,</li>\r\n	<li>Trainings at flexible schedule in our clients’ premises,</li>\r\n	<li>Dedicated Corporate Relations Coordinator to monitor the quality and feedback,</li>\r\n	<li>Competitive Corporate Prices.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Our Corporate Russian Courses</h2>\r\n<p>Our programs have been developed by a team of experienced language training professionals to meet you requirements in the following subject areas:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Regular Russian Courses (beginner to advanced),</li>\r\n	<li>Survival Russian (an intensive conversation course for those travelling to Russia soon),</li>\r\n	<li>Russian for Customer Service (adapted for hospitality, retail and other sectors),</li>\r\n	<li>Russian for Specific Purposes (sales, real estate, hospitality, oil and gas ),</li>\r\n	<li>Business Russian,</li>\r\n	<li>Tailor–made courses as per your company training objectives.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>We customize the content, the duration and the timings of our courses according to our clients’ learning objectives, schedule and participant background. Experienced, qualified and certified multi-lingual teachers and instructors will ensure smooth course delivery at our clients’ premises.  Proven methods and attention to detail produce tangible results.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>A specially appointed <strong>Corporate Relations Coordinator</strong> makes sure our clients’ requirements are well communicated and feedback is accounted for in the process of course delivery.\r\n</p>\r\n<h2>Competitive Corporate Rates</h2>\r\n<p>Since all our corporate courses are tailor-made we are adjusting our pricing to meet our clients’ budget requirements too. Please, send an e-mail to <a href=\"mailto:courses@headin.pro\">courses@headin.pro</a> to get your personalized quote.\r\n</p>','Corporate Russian Language Courses','','','2015-08-31 17:28:04','2015-09-13 20:26:18',1,'<div class=\"list-group\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/intensive-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Intensive Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/russian-language-for-children\" class=\"list-group-item\">Russian Language for Children</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/russian-test-preparation\" class=\"list-group-item\">Russian Test Preparation</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/regular-russian-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Regular Russian Courses</a>\r\n<a href=\"/en/courses/russian-language/corporate-russian-language-courses\" class=\"list-group-item\">Corporate Russian Language</a>',NULL);

